{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTTP","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTTP (The HyperText Transfer Protocol，超文本传输协议) 是用于在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/World_Wide_Web\">Web</a> 上传输超媒体文件的底层 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">协议</a> ，最典型场景的是在浏览器和服务器之间传递数据，以供人们浏览。现行的 HTTP 标准的版本是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP_2\">HTTP/2</a>。</p>\n<p><code>http://</code> 称为 <code>schema</code>，是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/URI\">URI</a> 的组成部分，一般位于网络地址的开头。以 <code>https://developer.mozilla.org</code> 为例，该地址说明请求文档时使用 HTTP 协议；这里的 https 代指 HTTP 协议的安全版本，即 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/SSL\">SSL</a> （或称 TLS）</p>\n<p>HTTP 是基于文本的 (所有的通信都以纯文本的形式进行) 以及无状态的 (当前通信状态不会发现以前的通信状态)，该特性极大方便了在 www 上浏览网页的人。除此之外，HTTP 也可以用于构建服务器之间交互的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/REST\">REST</a> web 服务，以及使得网站内容更加动态化的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/AJAX\">AJAX</a> 请求。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"补充知识","title":"补充知识","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>在 MDN 上的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP\">HTTP</a></li>\n  <li>在维基百科上的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B6%85%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTTP</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"补充知识","id":"补充知识"}],"summary":"HTTP (The HyperText Transfer Protocol，超文本传输协议) 是用于在 Web 上传输超媒体文件的底层 协议 ，最典型场景的是在浏览器和服务器之间传递数据，以供人们浏览。现行的 HTTP 标准的版本是 HTTP/2。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTTP","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTTP","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTTP","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTTP","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTTP","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTTP","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"HTTP","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTTP","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/http","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/http/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP","title":"HTTP"}],"pageTitle":"HTTP - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}